reviews.review_text: BIODTL Unbelievable bobby never sang it like this.

beat it down wow i never remember it like that .  i may have been alittle under the weather at these shows .  these are the shows right after bobs dog otis died so maybe he felt the need to add a little extra.  besides a 30 beat start woooooooow .  rest of the show is just good old grateful dead I geuss thats why we would go to every show  never know whats gonna happen
